## Limitations

The findings are based on available literature and may not encompass all perspectives or recent developments in workplace standards. The impact of universal standards can vary significantly across different industries and regions, which may not be fully captured in this report. Additionally, the dynamic nature of legal and ethical standards means that ongoing updates and reviews are necessary to maintain relevance and accuracy.